title: 43 Ways CRUELLA (2021) Is Just Like JOKER (2019)

Well Joker actually made Arthur a villain, Cruella just played it safe. I was pretty disappointed when Cruella didn't actually skin the dogs, that's literally what she's known for.
Cruella isnt her alter ego, Estella is. This was shown right at the very beginning because her not-real-mother asked Cruella to stop being her real self.
Joker didn’t skin puppies as a hobby
'Cruella' is a mix of 'The Devil Wears Prada' meets 'The Joker'.
